## ğŸ“Š Dataset

Dataset diambil dari **Kaggle**:

**Telco Customer Churn**  
ğŸ”— https://www.kaggle.com/blastchar/telco-customer-churn

Nama file yang digunakan:
WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv


Simpan file ke folder:
data/

---

## ğŸ§¹ Preprocessing Steps

1. Menghapus kolom `customerID`
2. Mengonversi `TotalCharges` (karena berisi whitespace)
3. One-hot encoding categorical features
4. Scaling numeric features (StandardScaler)
5. Trainâ€“test split 80/20

---

## ğŸ¤– Model

Model menggunakan:
- **LightGBM (Gradient Boosting)**  
- Parameter default + early stopping  
- Model disimpan sebagai artifact `.joblib`:
models/lgbm_churn.joblib


---

## ğŸ“ˆ Evaluation Metrics

Contoh metrik (akan berbeda sesuai hasil training Anda):
Accuracy: 0.83
Precision: 0.62
Recall: 0.58
F1-score: 0.60
ROC-AUC: 0.89


Detail lengkap tersimpan di:
models/metrics.json


---

## ğŸ‹ï¸ Training Locally

Aktifkan environment:

```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
# Mac/Linux: source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

Jalankan training:
python src/train.py

python src/train.py

Ini akan menghasilkan:

- models/lgbm_churn.joblib

- models/metrics.json

Run Streamlit Locally:
streamlit run app.py

Buka di browser:
http://localhost:8501

Deployment (Streamlit Cloud)

1. Push semua source code ke GitHub

2. Buka: https://share.streamlit.io

3. Klik New App

4. Pilih repo Anda

5. Select:

  - Branch: main

  - File: app.py

6. Klik Deploy

Aplikasi akan muncul sebagai URL publik seperti:
https://telco-churn-ml.streamlit.app/

Requirements:
streamlit
pandas
numpy
scikit-learn
lightgbm
joblib
matplotlib
shap
plotly

